Useful for anybody who needs a chinese-english dictionary

Very useful for anybody who uses mnemonics

DESIGN:

       Do you know you can read in Chinese?
 (Even before you have learned all the characters?) 


                                 The power reading method:

          Read                                    Understand                                  Remember
a story that keeps you captivated                  in an instant               with mnemonics to empower your memory


Look at the demo page to get the idea.

